name: CHEAPEST G1 BRISK CYMRIC GEN1
bio: Heyo! I'm CHEAPEST G1 BRISK CYMRIC GEN1. I'm a Skydiving Instructor by day, and I like talking about how much I lift by night. My great-great-great-great-great-great grandkitty lived with Amelia Earhart. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
